The sentence key 
Few-shot prompting clearly outperformed zero-shot across ChatGPT, Claude, and Gemini. 
The 3 examples helped the models understand exactly how to classify Complaint, Question, and Praise, 
which reduced mistakes on unclear messages.
Without examples, the models were less consistent and often mixed up similar tones.
This shows that giving the AI a few examples is the simplest way to make results more accurate and reliable.
